# === Allocate 16 MiB pool and split scratch / heap =================
# 16 MiB is the upper bound on input + output + label table size
# observed in the bootstrap chain (cc_riscv64.M1 + linker tables
# come close). First 2 KiB are scratch (token name compare),
# the rest is the heap used by label entries and output buffer.
